    <h1><a href="/"><i class="fa fa-instagram" style="position:relative;top:3px;"></i>&nbsp;Worried about the Instagram Shadowban?</a></h1>
    <p style="font-size:smaller;color:gray;margin:-10px 40px 40px 40px;">You're not alone! <strong>~4,500</strong> people are taking the test every hour since launch (Apr&nbsp;14,&nbsp;2017)</p>
    <form action="/" name="f1">
